text: The University of Nueva Caceres–Bataan is a university in Dinalupihan, Bataan, Philippines founded in 2014. It offers pre-school, elementary, and high school education. ==References== ==External links== *University of Nueva Caceres Category:Universities and colleges in Bataan Category:Educational institutions established in 2014 Category:University of Nueva Caceres Category:2014 establishments in the Philippines
